<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ại̹nãmā lilrãbĩ naḥ̊nu .. wah̊wa ʿanãạ qad̊ qaḍay̱
 yā turay̱ mimãn̊ nakẖāfu .. wabihi nil̊nā ạlrĩḍay̱

[V2]
 2- ại̹n̊ tufājī̊̉nā ạl̊balạyā .. ạảẘ tuhājim̊nā ạl̊kurūb̊
 nas̊tamidã ạl̊ʿaẘna min̊hu .. nar̊taqi faẘqa ạl̊kẖuṭūb̊

[V3]
 3- walanā qad̊ ṣāra fīhi .. kulũ sẖaẙʾiⁿ fal̊nusar̃̊
 falanā naṣ̊ruⁿ fī ḍīqiⁿ .. wāḍ̊ṭihādiⁿ ạảẘ kẖaṭar̊

[V4]
 4- naḥ̊nu fī ẓilĩ ḥimāhu .. mā ạlãdẖī yur̊hibunā
 kaẙfa nakẖ̊sẖay̱ min̊ ʿadūiⁿ̃ .. wahūa yaḥ̊faẓunā

[V5]
 5- qad̊ daʿānā ḥas̊ba qaṣ̊diⁿ .. muj̊zilạaⁿ niʿ̊matahu
 līakūna ạl̊kulũ fīhi .. musẖ̊bihaⁿạ ṣūratahu

[V6]
 6- ại̹nãnā ḥat̊maⁿạ sanam̊lik̊ .. maʿ̊hu fī ạảs̊may̱ ạlrũbūʿ̊
 wanakūnu kulã ḥīniⁿ .. maʿ̊ ḥabībinā yasūʿ̊</lyrics>
<title>ạ̹nmạ llrb nḥn</title>
</song>